Place the asparagus in a large bowl. Add the lettuce, sprouts, mushrooms, and pepper. Add the spaghetti or Chinese noodles. Sprinkle with the scallions, ginger, and garlic; toss gently. Place the peanut butter in a medium bowl. Stir in the broth. Whisk in the vinegar, soy sauce, honey, oil, and chili sauce. Pour over the salad and toss.